text: Nils Grönvall (15 May 1894 - 13 July 1983) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual foil event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish foil fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lund
